@{
    ViewBag.Title = "How To Play";
}
<h2>@ViewBag.Title.</h2>


<p>
    <h3>Create an account</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Click Register</li>
        <li>Create a user, entering in your email and password</li>
        <img src="~/Images/Createuser.png" />
    </ul>

    <h3>Create or Join a pool</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>If you want to create a new pool, click 'Create new pool'</li>
        <img src="~/Images/CreateJoinPool.png" />
        <ul>
            <li>To create a new pool, enter in a name for the pool</li>
            <li>Then select which games will be part of your pool. By default all games are selected</li>
            <li>Click the create button at the bottom of the page</li>
            <img src="~/Images/CreatePool.png" />
            <li>This will create a pool, and assign an invitation code that others can use to join your pool</li>
            <img src="~/Images/PoolWithCode.png" />
        </ul>
        <li>You received an invitation code from a friend, click 'Join a private pool'</li>
        <li>Enter the invitation code</li>
        <img src="~/Images/JoinPool.png" />
        <li>Once you have joined, the pool will be listed under 'Your Pools'</li>
        It is possible to join multiple pools.
    </ul>

    <h3><b>Select a winning team...</b></h3>
    <ul>
        <li>
            First, browse to
            @Html.ActionLink("My Picks", "MyPicks", "Picks").
        </li>
        <li>If you are a member of multiple pools, use the drop down list to switch between them</li>

        <li>
            To assist with selecting your teams and assigning the ranking score, you can use the printable worksheet by clicking the link at the top of the page
        </li>
        <img src="~/Images/PrintableWorksheet.png" />
        <li>Then click on the name of the team you predict will win that bowl game.</li>        
        <li>Your choice will be identified with a thumbs up icon.</li>        
        <img src="~/Images/TeamSelected.png" />
    </ul>

    <h3><b>Change your Ranking Score...</b></h3>
    <ul id="list">
        <li>
            You must enter your confidence score for each game in the appropriate textbox.
        </li>
        <img src="~/Images/ConfidenceScore.png" />
        <li>
            After entering your confidence score for all the games, click 'Save Changes'.
        </li>
    </ul>
    <h3><b>Save your changes</b></h3>
    <ul>
        <li>
            When ready, be sure to save your changes. Click the Save Changes button at the top or bottom of the
            @Html.ActionLink("My Picks", "MyPicks", "Picks") page.
        </li>
        
        <img src="~/Images/SaveChanges.png" />
        <li>If there are errors with your selections, you will see one or more messages at the top of the page.</li>
        <img src="~/Images/ValidationError.png" />
    </ul>

    <h3><b>Track your progress</b></h3>
    <ul>
        <li>
            Once the games have started, you can see how you did on individual game by going back to the
            @Html.ActionLink("My Picks", "MyPicks", "Picks") page.
        </li>
        
        <li>Here, you can see when each game is scheduled to be played.</li>
        
        <li>When the game is over, you can see the final score and how many points you were awarded.</li>
        
        @*<li>Below you can see that we picked the correct winner for the Gildan New Mexico Bowl and were awarded 2 points.</li>
        
        <li>We did not pick the correct winner of the Royal Purple Las Vegas Bowl and were awarded 0 points.</li>*@
        
        <img src="~/Images/MyPicksProgress.png" />
        <li>The percentages to the right indicate the percent of players in your pool that picked that team to be the winner</li>
        <li>
            You can also track your overall progress on the
            @Html.ActionLink("Leaderboard", "Leaderboard", "Picks").
        </li>
    </ul>

</p>
